data.text:
About this school

Woodburn Elementary School is a suburban public school in Falls Church, Virginia that is part of Fairfax County Public Schools. It serves 486 students in Pre-K - 6 with a student/teacher ratio of 12.8:1. Its teachers have had 33 projects funded on DonorsChoose.
